Package util.analytics

The analytics package contains classes that analyze parameters of the simulation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PassengerAnalyzer
    A passenger analyzer analyzes the behaviour of passengers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivityDistributionAnalyzer
    A parameter tracker for the distribution of activities of passengers.
    AgentNumberAnalyzer
    A parameter tracker for the agent numbers.
    Analytics
    Analytics module of the simulation.
    Analyzer
    A parameter tracker tracks parameters.
    DistanceAnalyzer
    Tracks the average distance covered by passengers.
    MissedFlightsAnalyzer
    A parameter tracker for missed flights.
    QueueAnalyzer
    A queue parameter tracker updates value for a queue line graph.
    TimeInQueueAnalyzer
    A time in queue parameter tracker keeps track of the average time that passengers spent in the queues.
    TimeToGateAnalyzer
    Determines the average time to gate for all passengers.
    TimeToGatePerFlightAnalyzer
    A Time To Gate Per Flight Parameter Tracker indicates the average times to gate for the different flights.

Package util.analytics Description

The analytics package contains classes that analyze parameters of the simulation. They estimate efficiency, security and other parameters of a simulation.
Author:
S.A.M. Janssen
